{"tid":104461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【60歲灰姑娘】婚後先知老公係杜拜富豪 每月有220萬零用","createTime":"2017-02-02T06:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T08:18:06.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c29da0d2c8e49d6d1425b8c60097758afdf30f79","tid":104461,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170202/56246613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170202%2F56246613&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=95fd8527\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170202%2F56246613&h=df7b4572\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170202/56246613</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國一名60歲失婚婦人喜迎第二春，但令她意想不到的是，當她再披嫁衣時發現新任丈夫是杜拜富豪，自此她的生活變得不一樣，盡享榮華富貴，單單每月的零用錢便有1,000萬泰銖（220萬港元），堪稱是現實版灰姑娘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170201/large/1485926157_6b2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170201%2Flarge%2F1485926157_6b2e.jpg&h=3562f710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n60歲的穆娜以前在泰國開小型旅行社，跟前夫離婚後，認識了一位到泰國旅遊的杜拜遊客，兩人很合得來，該男子返回杜拜後仍經常打長途電話與她談情，就這樣兩人發展異地戀，交往4、5年後決定結婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170201/large/1485931010_1bd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170201%2Flarge%2F1485931010_1bd8.jpg&h=74495de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怎料她3年前結婚才知道丈夫是杜拜五大富豪之一，富可敵國。她每月的零用有220萬港元，家中猶如皇宮般，有16人隨身伺候，令她可以過着猶如童話公主般的生活。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170201/large/1485926156_eac5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170201%2Flarge%2F1485926156_eac5.jpg&h=d2908840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過穆娜起初不習慣要與另外四房「分享」丈夫，她說：「剛開始不習慣，一來我英文不好，二來要學會與老公的四位老婆相處，不過在他寵愛下，我很快就融入新家庭&hellip;&hellip;我現在甚麼都不需要做，只要將自己打扮得漂亮、逛逛街、美容打扮和出席晚會活動。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170201/large/1485931011_02cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170201%2Flarge%2F1485931011_02cb.jpg&h=71c25f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n穆娜又指，雖然丈夫很富有，但不容許他再娶第六個老婆，否則她會提出離婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170201/large/1485926158_7b17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170201%2Flarge%2F1485926158_7b17.jpg&h=fd12359b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60cff49d23ce805dda7b361f16e793da5fc3aec1","tid":104461,"uid":31254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"穆娜又指，雖然丈夫很富有，但不容許他再娶第六個老婆，否則她會提出離婚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64be72928e8849e5c13a1374ebd81fc7165587c","tid":104461,"uid":81323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T06:39:37.000Z","msg":"富豪應該有風濕重要幾嚴下"},{"pid":"98d478e3bece54a10c7624caf2906b12cc311ade","tid":104461,"uid":18540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T06:45:32.000Z","msg":"有鳩的妖魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f2043972ac7581e29037134fa45a66b043f1f5","tid":104461,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}